♪<i> Springfield built a wall</i> ♪
♪<i> The Who played on the top</i> ♪

00:54.355 --> 00:56.021
♪<i> Carl, Lenny, Barney, Moe</i> ♪

00:56.023 --> 00:57.856
♪<i> And a fat bald guy</i>
<i> who hollers "d'oh"</i> ♪

00:57.858 --> 01:01.427
♪<i> It all started</i>
<i> with</i> The Simpsons,<i> d'oh! ♪</i>

